Package: krpoltext
Title: Korean Political Text Corpora for Reproducible Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tae Hyun", "Lim", , "tlim@hamilton.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0429-2683"))
    )
Description: Provides easy access to two large-scale Korean political text
    corpora described in Lim (2025) <doi:10.1038/s41597-025-05220-4>:
    (1) South Korean Election Campaign Booklets covering 49,678 candidates
    across presidential, National Assembly, and local elections (2000-2022),
    and (2) South Korean Party Statements containing 82,723 official
    statements from the two major parties (2003-2022). Functions support
    loading, querying, caching, and converting data for text analysis
    workflows with 'quanteda' and 'tidytext'.
